{"tid":368263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休假期間中環墮樓　威院麻醉科女醫生命危","createTime":"2017-08-21T11:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T18:48:05.000Z","uid":13468,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc1cb26585225cb656e3ab48f3d550d341ef82f","tid":368263,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:57:22.000Z","msg":"休假期間中環墮樓　威院麻醉科女醫生命危 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中環美利道多層停車場對開，今早有人墮下，途人發現後報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方指涉事者為36歲女子，她腳部受傷送院。警員接報到場時，傷者昏迷，其後轉送瑪麗醫院治理，警方於現場檢獲遺書，初步調查相信她從上址停車場墮下，事件沒有可疑，女子情況危殆，案件列作「企圖自殺」。據了解涉事女子因工作問題不開心。<br />\n<br />\n威爾斯親王醫院發言人下午回覆本報查詢，證實該名墮樓者為威院麻醉科副顧問醫生，現時正值休假。院方指對事件深感難過，會盡力為該員工及其家人提供一切可行支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170821/s00001/1503312792424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170821%2Fs00001%2F1503312792424&d=J17Pb8Nc4BJ8oR5zhWyiLxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=15e39c02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170821%2Fs00001%2F1503312792424&h=4e8f4004\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170821/s00001/1503312792424</a>"},{"pid":"fd21649c493260e5fb6ecaffec06936ac27278c1","tid":368263,"uid":48266,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"佢都要死<br />\n我死十次都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d807851e5e9c102f2fe5f59a69d439d85b1233e2","tid":368263,"uid":45148,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"香港自殺風氣<br />\n無分貧富"},{"pid":"3e8c7b08f5fa404f805eadada50c073a234a6932","tid":368263,"uid":29609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"醫生都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49c33d1adc52d6a9f81a1d2d85f01174ea4a2e3","tid":368263,"uid":102