br />\n話出就出?<br />\n出到黎就無壓力?</blockquote><br />\n壓力都有, 不過一定細好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左，竟然覺得壓力細好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先人地係麻醉科醫生，唔係麻醉師<br />\n係冇麻醉師哩樣野<br />\n冇佢既話，你手術都唔洗做可以直接推入殮房<br />\n以為人地真係打藥比你咁簡單？<br />\n係手術室入面條友透唔透到氣，血壓心跳上落，大流血，淨係得佢會理，外科醫生係完全唔會理<br />\n成間醫院入面如果有人透唔到氣要插喉，其他科醫生搞唔到就要搵麻醉科，連麻醉科都插唔到就要界頸架啦<br />\n做既所有決定其實好影響病人既生死<br />\n<br />\n出私家以為真係好好？<br />\n冇人會backup你<br />\n所有野要自己搞掂晒<br />\n做唔到既話條友係可以即時死係你面前死<br />\n出事既話要全部自己負責，冇HA幫你<br />\n賺既錢分分鐘都唔夠你賠<br />\n所以麻醉科係屬於高風險類，保險咁貴</blockquote><br />\n咪戇鳩啦，冇麻醉師呢樣野，不嬲都係咁稱呼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www3.ha.org.hk/qeh/department/anae_ots/zh-hk/html/patientinformation/patientinformationfaq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.ha.org.hk%2Fqeh%2Fdepartment%2Fanae_ots%2Fzh-hk%2Fhtml%2Fpatientinformation%2Fpatientinformationfaq.html&d=J17Pb8Nc4BJ8oR5zhWyiLxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2f064641\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.ha.org.hk/qeh/department/anae_ots/zh-hk/html/patientinformation/patientinformationfaq.html</a></blockquote><br />\n中文譯名就來其啦<br />\n香港用開英文名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通人點會用英文名呀，你阿媽細個帶你睇醫生會話去睇pediatric doctor？"},{"pid":"af855fc994235f43e2e5e4f52266a079898edfee","tid":368263,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T02:30:42.000Z","msg":"我鄉下隻狗.jpg"},{"pid":"3088c3ef82a1c80927dd5fb845be1a819be1e977","tid":368263,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:46:30.000Z","msg":"好似精神科醫生自殺率最高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be180e7ab296e9aa14b8dca4fc7e4c8ffbe65c84","tid":368263,"uid":41849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"香港醫生乜權都拿哂都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bb86e9d4a671883e0b4f4453cd6a61fe4fa274","tid":368263,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下點解大出血都係得麻醉科醫生理<br />\n外科唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324355d8b05a99c0fed3c716dfeef23cf5246a4c","tid":368263,"uid":16777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T07:05:12.000Z","msg":"竟然仲有人覺得十幾萬一個月就無壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 人地專業醫生黎架 每一個決定都係人命關鍵 你估係保險倫敦金咁啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6dc0b966dfd2a80bde4018e9fad8c6c8dde4dab","tid":368263,"uid":26529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下點解大出血都係得麻醉科醫生理<br />\n外科唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係話外科醫生會用刀幫個病人止血<br />\nE.g. 扎左條血管，切左流血嘅器官,etc.<br />\n麻醉科就係外科醫生止血嘅時候幫佢地吊住病人條命<br />\nE.g. 瘋狂輸血，比藥幫手止血， 吊強心針咁"},{"pid":"3d5c2526bfeab874822fc7619e0d60f45864283d","tid":368263,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該唔關工作壓力事<br />\n<br />\n佢係醫院頂唔順大不了咪自己出黎掛牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話出就出?<br />\n出到黎就無壓力?</blockquote><br />\n壓力都有, 不過一定細好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左，竟然覺得壓力細好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先人地係麻醉科醫生，唔係麻醉師<br />\n係冇麻醉師哩樣野<br />\n冇佢既話，你手術都唔洗做可以直接推入殮房<br />\n以為人地真係打藥比你咁簡單？<br />\n係手術室入面條友透唔透到氣，血壓心跳上落，大流血，淨係得佢會理，外科醫生係完全唔會理<br />\n成間醫院入面如果有人透唔到氣要插喉，其他科醫生搞唔到就要搵麻醉科，連麻醉科都插唔到就要界頸架啦<br />\n做既所有決定其實好影響病人既生死<br />\n<br />\n出私家以為真係好好？<br />\n冇人會backup你<br />\n所有野要自己搞掂晒<br />\n做唔到既話條友係可以即時死係你面前死<br />\n出事既話要全部自己負責，冇HA幫你<br />\n賺既錢分分鐘都唔夠你賠<br />\n所以麻醉科係屬於高風險類，保險咁貴</blockquote><br />\n咪戇鳩啦，冇麻醉師呢樣野，不嬲都係咁稱呼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www3.ha.org.hk/qeh/department/anae_ots/zh-hk/html/patientinformation/patientinformationfaq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.ha.org.hk%2Fqeh%2Fdepartment%2Fanae_ots%2Fzh-hk%2Fhtml%2Fpatientinformation%2Fpatientinformationfaq.html&d=J17Pb8Nc4BJ8oR5zhWyiLxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2f064641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www3.ha.org.hk/qeh/department/anae_ots/zh-hk/html/patientinformation/patientinformationfaq.html</a></blockquote><br />\n其實專業人仕, 自已可能有買專業責任保險 ?"},{"pid":"50a03e25590cf9a94f3103bf38851323ac2aca2f","tid":368263,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生一向都大壓力<br />\n一次失誤即刻無得撈 死左人自己又良心責備<br />\n一份工要零失誤係幾咁大壓力</blockquote><br />\n冇可能零失誤. <br />\n我自已做醫院工, 呢排做緊d project , 都有醫生d report 睇漏野. <br />\n問題只係, 果樣野未必會死人咁解"},{"pid":"296f343d1d3d18b4de0fa6e3a4672330e6653d65","tid":368263,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該唔關工作壓力事<br />\n<br />\n佢係醫院頂唔順大不了咪自己出黎掛牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話出就出?<br />\n出到黎就無壓力?</blockquote><br />\n壓力都有, 不過一定細好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左，竟然覺得壓力細好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先人地係麻醉科醫生，唔係麻醉師<br />\n係冇麻醉師哩樣野<br />\n冇佢既話，你手術都唔洗做可以直接推入殮房<br />\n以為人地真係打藥比你咁簡單？<br />\n係手術室入面條友透唔透到氣，血壓心跳上落，大流血，淨係得佢會理，外科醫生係完全唔會理<br />\n成間醫院入面如果有人透唔到氣要插喉，其他科醫生搞唔到就要搵麻醉科，連麻醉科都插唔到就要界頸架啦<br />\n做既所有決定其實好影響病人既生死<br />\n<br />\n出私家以為真係好好？<br />\n冇人會backup你<br />\n所有野要自己搞掂晒<br />\n做唔到既話條友係可以即時死係你面前死<br />\n出事既話要全部自己負責，冇HA幫你<br />\n賺既錢分分鐘都唔夠你賠<br />\n所以麻醉科係屬於高風險類，保險咁貴</blockquote><br />\n咪戇鳩啦，冇麻醉師呢樣野，不嬲都係咁稱呼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www3.ha.org.hk/qeh/department/anae_ots/zh-hk/html/patientinformation/patientinformationfaq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.ha.org.hk%2Fqeh%2Fdepartment%2Fanae_ots%2Fzh-hk%2Fhtml%2Fpatientinformation%2Fpatientinformationfaq.html&d=J17Pb8Nc4BJ8oR5zhWyiLxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2f064641\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.ha.org.hk/qeh/department/anae_ots/zh-hk/html/patientinformation/patientinformationfaq.html</a></blockquote><br />\n中文譯名就來其啦<br />\n香港用開英文名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通人點會用英文名呀，你阿媽細個帶你睇醫生會話去睇pediatric doctor？</blockquote><br />\npediatrician <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d6e2492535ed18d3fd09cd36725763e3db432f","tid":368263,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T09:59:35.000Z","msg":"咁撚多支那人落嚟用醫療資源<br />\n香港又人口老化多左廢老<br />\n實大壓力啦"},{"pid":"abec3253fa05af4e2b5c3967c0becb55457dffa7","tid":368263,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T22:07:46.000Z","msg":"一死了知, 好撚有型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你頂唔撚順就當初咪撚讀, 得你工作就大壓力.<br />\n浪費左果一年個學位, 因為你條柒頭既出現有一個人無得讀. <br />\n<br />\n有 D 做老闆既公司失敗員工同佢家屬乞米係咪慘? 救生員睇住你班撚屌死都要游, 有事要出去救你又係咪慘? 消防員入火場, 唔撚只被困者連自己兄弟都要睇住慘唔慘?<br />\n<br />\n六位數收得多過上面班 &quot;基層&quot;, 壓力大過佢地? 你係高分低能定點?  <br />\n<br />\n成個社會點撚樣栽培你, 你無朋友架? 你就爽啦就撚左. <br />\n留低班就冚家富啦, 佢地既人生有一點就係你條撚樣瓜左. 我屋企就有兩個親眼見到, 同小學最好朋友自殺死佢地一個抑鬱一個自始開燈訓密室恐懼, 慘唔慘?<br />\n<br />\n上面講到有班人死就大撚晒, 家下訓家果班受風受雨有無死撚晒呀? 返工大壓力咪唔撚做囉? 比物慾控制住 downgrade 唔到?<br />\n<br />\n除非你病撚到果 d 絕症果隻咁, 連身邊人都覺得你去左係好事. 唔係你自殺根本就係浪費. 一係你就做義士幫香港返正軌先死.  聽落好撚難聽但事實永遠奀耳."},{"pid":"ab7c5b068d7e4f397ebdfb42182ea442a9c3911f","tid":368263,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>工作壓力大<br />\n<br />\n有d醫生患咗焦慮症或抑鬱症，唔敢求醫，自己偷偷食藥....<br />\n<br />\n食picamilon/phenibut</blockquote><br />\n呢兩隻藥香港有approval?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過近幾年有隻治療GAD新藥Lyrica (pregabalin)上市，類似picamilon/phenibut都係GABA receptor modulator ，起效快，一個星期就可控制住焦慮感，人會變得開朗，健談........ 唔會好似BZD個類藥物食到懵盛盛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似唔少連登仔都食緊Lyrica"},{"pid":"18957ba434e62bf18b12c5379cb91eab5899d122","tid":368263,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dcd766e7ce3e60c32955abe21ea84688c6759c","tid":368263,"uid":26529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>工作壓力大<br />\n<br />\n有d醫生患咗焦慮症或抑鬱症，唔敢求醫，自己偷偷食藥....<br />\n<br />\n食picamilon/phenibut</blockquote><br />\n呢兩隻藥香港有approval?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過近幾年有隻治療GAD新藥Lyrica (pregabalin)上市，類似picamilon/phenibut都係GABA receptor modulator ，起效快，一個星期就可控制住焦慮感，人會變得開朗，健談........ 唔會好似BZD個類藥物食到懵盛盛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似唔少連登仔都食緊Lyrica</blockquote><br />\nPregabalin 同gabapentin好似都係calcium channel blocker<br />\n反而benzo先係gaba receptor modulator<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed86d8e5897d53c876d2a68124acf8ace41dc3c","tid":368263,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:22:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98cbfd66498c3e9275312a14926e6fa2dd2701fa","tid":368263,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d69c26f5a1c5527246cbe0dbc5ab884ac9b8e7ce","tid":368263,"uid":49727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:15:31.000Z",