ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T18:43:54.000Z","msg":"還是歐洲做爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}